CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. A17 reads: "Patio Chatter was enjoyed by this quintet at the breakfast hosted by the William Fredericks after the Frogs' formal. Left to right: Mrs. Christopher Jeffries and Dr. Jeffries of Altoona; Mrs. Arthur Catlin and Mr. Catlin, Cleveland, Ohio, and Mrs. Margaret Williams of Philadelphia. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Dr. and Mrs. Christopher Jeffries, Mr. and Mrs. Arthur Catlin, and Margaret Williams, seated at table under patio umbrella for FROGS breakfast
